Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:02.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的宿愿就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:07.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了虫奉行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:36.16,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在八丈岛闭关的虫奉行大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:39.18,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被名为虫狩的组织盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:46.16,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟大人 这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:52.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们市街巡逻组 加上武家巡逻组
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:56.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及寺社巡逻组都急速奔赴实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:58.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江户的守卫将会…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.33,0:02:00.38,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 仁兵卫君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:03.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一虫奉行大人有所不测
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.05,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江户将会在一夜之间变成无人荒野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:09.45,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 江…江户会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:17.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【虫狩强袭 八丈岛事变】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:21.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:28.91,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一艘大船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:32.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是虫奉行所专用的大型弁才船哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:32.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}【弁才船：中世末期至明治时期 日本国内海运广为使用的大型木造帆船】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.76,0:02:34.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即启航
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:42.18,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏在这种时候出现了巨虫…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:46.81,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边是… 小春小姐住处附近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:52.95,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间了 立即启航
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:57.49,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 那只虫怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:03:03.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们当下的职责 是保护虫奉行大人免受奸徒所害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:07.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了 这段时间只好请各位以大局为重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:09.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.41,0:03:15.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你很痛苦 可现在我们有其他要务在身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:23.14,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:32.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此等琐事 就交由吾等武家巡逻组吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.17,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾上大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:40.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区虫子 竟敢在大将军脚下撒野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:42.76,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是岂有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:46.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾上影忠率领的武家巡逻组全组
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:51.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘为将军大人效犬马之劳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:57.07,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾上大人 江户就拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.04,0:04:03.44,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么出发吧 各位 目的地是八丈岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的宿愿就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:23.27,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了虫奉行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已能隐约看见岛屿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:47.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐 那就是八丈岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:50.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫奉行大人就在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:01.69,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:05.37,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未那蚕 果然是你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:10.64,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒做先锋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:51.84,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:57.49,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 居然与无涯势均力敌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:04.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是无涯大人… 你到底是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:14.63,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 无涯 竟然对这些家伙守口如瓶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:19.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是未那蚕 虫狩的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫狩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:24.94,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没劲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:29.49,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好这会儿同伴们正要杀虫奉行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:33.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  目的是要杀虫奉行大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 无涯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.39,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫狩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:58.36,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害你母亲的 是名为虫狩的一伙人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:05.84,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前 杀害恋川左之助的妻子阿菊的 是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:08.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:16.84,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你们逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.18,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:40.49,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.61,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火钵 仁兵卫君 你们先行前往
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:48.63,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:49.76,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:51.27,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:02.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的 可一个都别想走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:11.09,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 其实早就想死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:14.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个荒谬无伦的世界上生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:17.03,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说 就跟受刑一般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:24.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 为了尽快除掉虫奉行以求解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:27.42,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打扫垃圾来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:37.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快我就能与这个世界说再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:44.76,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 能杀了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:55.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 杀害阿菊的人是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:02.51,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在朝着哪里开炮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:06.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞄得可相当准
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:24.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 炮弹的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:32.37,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 还死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:52.40,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能因为宰了条杂鱼 就要收回我「九十九人斩」的名号啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:57.49,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.06,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋川君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:08.43,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快走吧 小鸟酱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:27.29,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是有可疑之人潜入这座岛上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:39.38,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了 八丈岛上的生灵们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:43.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:47.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 老大 你害怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫子停止鸣叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:53.92,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫子都…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:02.52,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是毒雾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:06.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 服下解药
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:14.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 虫奉行就在这毒雾深处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:22.18,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月岛 你在抓哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:23.61,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:26.34,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放 会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:30.77,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐 那瘴气是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.34,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:33.83,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬紧牙关上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.99,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是头阵前锋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:39.37,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火钵小姐 放心交给在下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:45.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我月岛仁兵卫粉身碎骨也不会拖火钵小姐后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:48.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 你在捏什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:57.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人就是【虫狩】
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月岛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:14.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.63,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:35.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在虫奉行所里见过的那位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:42.52,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:44.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在此处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:47.83,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为您是虫奉行大人的侍女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:55.34,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侍女小姐 抱歉 情况紧急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:57.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫奉行大人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:58.66,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:00.03,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:02.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫奉行大人是外出了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.52,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:07.08,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:11.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侍女小姐现在也正准备要到虫奉行大人那里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:17.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:22.07,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 实际就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:26.18,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:31.17,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些叫【虫狩】的人马上就会到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:33.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是来要虫奉行大人的命的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:35.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:39.80,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里被毒雾包围 不会有人能到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.83,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:44.26,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 虫奉行大人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:47.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:50.45,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他待在一个安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.65,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫阳花玉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下一下地来 很麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:20.55,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆破竟然被她用踢出的冲击波抵消了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:22.84,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是【虫狩】的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:24.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑八怪白痴女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:26.17,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑 丑八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:28.36,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 你个贫乳眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:32.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是自己找死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:34.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲脚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:46.37,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫奉行大人就是在这样一个毫无生气的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:51.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自一人渡过夏天的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:58.67,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 侍女小姐 虫奉行大人究竟是个怎样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:02.42,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 说一些也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:04.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫奉行是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:08.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下觉得 他一定是身材魁梧 孔武有力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:11.73,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像个修行僧一样严于律己的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:15.61,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:17.40,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.17,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 随他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:21.43,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是那样强大的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:25.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能耐住独自一人呆在这种地方的寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:36.86,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能 虫奉行他一点都不感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:41.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而想一直待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:44.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于虫奉行来说 自由是奢侈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:48.39,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在江户 哪怕要从竹帘后面出来也是件难事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:54.69,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 至少在这里只要抬起头就能望见天空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:03.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 在下不太明白您刚刚说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:06.37,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有一点 在下可以很确定地说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:09.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起独自在这里看到的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:11.94,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在江户和大家一起看到的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:14.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更能给人力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:23.12,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人 一直都是抱着这样的想法仰望天空的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:29.04,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着这样想法的人 真是让人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:34.99,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫奉行他 如果能有你这样的人在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:38.09,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许就不会感到那么寂寞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于见面了 虫奉行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:54.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:12.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸性毒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:13.63,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:18.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:32.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾在逐渐消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:49.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想再往前踏一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:55.38,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手是用刀高手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.62,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害你母亲的凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:01.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是【虫狩】那伙人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:03.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【虫狩】
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:07.84,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也应该隐隐有所发觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:12.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种刀法 不是相当的高手是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:20.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 只会放枪的小喽啰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:23.99,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是母亲的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:27.12,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天间 这里就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:29.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:31.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急急如律令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:34.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为吉 全力一击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:41.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,末吉 急急如律令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:45.72,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为我还会吃这招吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:52.34,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,末吉 为吉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:58.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候做个了结了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.94,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 虫狩们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:06.42,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始由我月岛仁兵卫来当你们的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.75,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侍女小姐 您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 就请交给在下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:14.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您即刻赶到到虫奉行大人那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:16.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运为何如此捉弄人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:21.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本不愿将你牵连进来 方才有意拉开与你的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:24.69,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:28.03,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了 虫狩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:31.62,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:37.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:43.55,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人又再… 要赶紧离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:54.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样都挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:57.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:59.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与以往明显不同的心神不宁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:04.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有要来杀我的虫狩们在场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:06.86,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却在意着其他的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.46,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:12.52,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侍女小姐 您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:13.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:20.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才起 我就一直在记挂着这个叫月岛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:35.17,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 无涯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:39.29,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会有和你兵刃相见的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:51.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘剑 血飞溅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:59.04,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身手好像并没有生疏掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:02.08,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是虫狩的前任首领
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:15.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无涯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:19.14,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「虫狩的首领」是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:21.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:26.17,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我母亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:04.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洁白的花 洁白的砂子 洁白的波涛 洁白的云彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:07.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 在那里飘着的是火钵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.41,0:23:08.88,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白色的吧 你的兜裆布
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:10.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…谁让你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:14.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 虫奉行 黑扬羽降临
